Chief Financial Officer (CFO) [Jakarta - Indonesia]
Responsibilities
Bachelor and master degree in finance or accounting from reputable university.Maximum age 45 years old.Minimum 5 years of senior-management responsibility in finance plus several years of auditing experience in big-four public accounting firms.Previous exposure with energy or telecommunication or retail business is preferred.Familiarity with project finance, debt/ equity financing, IFRS, and financial statement consolidation, and general taxation, is required.Fluency in English is required; fluency in Mandarin is an advantage. With a vision of becoming a leading energy and infrastructure company in Indonesia,we are looking for high-potential candidates to be employed for the Chief Financial Officer positionat our company or subsidiaries or affiliates. Interested candidates can send the resume and photograph by e-mail tohrdirector@dss.co.id  no later than May 31, 2014.Only short-listed candidates will be contacted for further selection process.More information about DSS can be found at www.dss.co.id
